  Peng5-iu2, li2 si7 sin3 Ia5-sou--e5 a2 m7-si7? Li2 si7 sin3-tou5 a2 m7-si7? Li2 na7 chin-chiaN3 si7 sin3-tou5, chhiaN2 koh soe3-ji7 siuN7, tau3-ti2 siaN2 si5 bat an2-ni kap Ia5-sou kong2-oe7? Kiam2-chhai2 chit8 ni5 cheng5, chit8 geh8 cheng5, a2-si7 chit8 jit8 cheng5? Kiu3-keng3 u7 loa7-choe7 pai2? ChhiaN2 li2 seng in3 chiah-e5 bun7-toe5......Khi3 le2-pai3-tng5 le2-pai3 thiaN lang5 e5 ki5-to2, te3 lang5 gim5-si, kap peng5-iu2 tang5 chit8 ui7 ki5-to2, che long2 si7 iong5-iN7 e5 su7, si7 lan2 sou2 choe3 oe7 kau3--e5, tok8-tok8 lan2 kan-ta si5-si5 an2-ni, chiu7 oe7 khi3-sak phaiN2 than3 ho2 a2 boe7? Li2 an2-ni choe3 su7 chiu7 sng3 beng5-pek8 a2 m7 si7? Peng5-iu2--ah, chiau3 an2-ni khi3 choe3, ku2 si7 thoe3 lang5 le2-pai3, ki5-to2, thoe3 lang5 o-lo2 ki5-kiu5, long2-chong2 si7 ka7 lang5 choe3, ai3 hou7 ho2 khoaN3 ho2 thiaN na7-tiaN7. Li2 m7-si7 ui7 pun2-sin kiu5, ui7 pun2-sin gim5. M7-thang chho3 siuN7 cheng3-lang5 chu7-chip8 le2-pai3, ki5-to2, m7 si7 kap Ia5-sou kau-poe5 kong2-oe7, phah-sng3 si7 thoe3 Ia5-sou thoan5 hok-im, thoe3 Ia5-sou ka3-si7 cheng3 lang5, a2-si7 thoe3 Ia5-sou choe3 kang, m7-ku2 chiah-e5 ku2-tong7 long2 m7 si7 kap Ia5-sou kau-poe5 kong2-oe7. Siat-su2 li2 tui3 thiN-kng kau3 jit8-am3 choe3 Siong7-te3 sou2 ai3 li2 choe3--e5, siat-su2 li2 khian5-seng5, chiong li2 e5 si5-kan, chiN5-chai5, sim-su long2-chong2 hian3 hou7 Siong7-te3, thoe3 I choe3 kang, tioh8 chai na7 bo5 kap Ia5-sou kau-poe5 kong2-oe7, chiu7 li2 sou2 jiat8-sim--e5, boe7 sng3 choe3 kap Ia5-sou kau-poe5. Li2 na7 chit8 jit8 bo5 eng7 tam7-poh8-a2 si5-kan, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 kap Ia5-sou kau-poe5, li2 chiu7 u7 chin toa7 gui5-hiam2, li2 e5 sou2 choe3 tek-khak u7 chin toa7 e5 chho3-gou7. Na7 chit8 jit8 kap Ia5-sou ong2-lai5, chiu7 chai li2 peng5-si5 sou2 choe3 e5 kang long2 bo5 kong-hau7, hit si5 li2 chiu7 oe7 chai kap li2 e5 Kiu3-chu2 iau2-be7 saN-bat, Ia5-sou m7-bat--li2, li2 iah8 m7-bat Ia5-sou, li2 tek-khak chin ki5-koai3. 
